# BitAgora POS - Website Page Templates
## Marketing & Content Pages Using Application Styling

### **Overview**
These templates extend the application's design system to marketing and content pages, ensuring complete visual consistency between the website and the application.

---

## **ðŸŽ¨ Shared Design System**

### **Same Color Palette & Typography**
All website pages use the **identical styling system** as the application:
- **Background**: `#0f172a` (same dark theme)
- **Primary**: `#60a5fa` (same blue accent)
- **Typography**: Same font system and sizing
- **Components**: Same button styles, form elements, cards

### **Website-Specific Adaptations**
- **Marketing focus**: Hero sections, feature grids, pricing tables
- **Content structure**: Headers, navigation, footers
- **Call-to-action**: Conversion-optimized buttons leading to registration

---

## **ðŸ“‹ Template 1: Landing Page**

### **Layout Structure**
```tsx
Page Container:
- Full viewport: `min-h-screen bg-background`
- Header: `sticky top-0 z-50 bg-background/80 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-border`
- Main content: `flex-1`
- Footer: `bg-card border-t border-border`

Header Navigation:
- Container: `max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 h-16 flex items-center justify-between`
- Logo: `<Zap className="h-8 w-8 text-primary" />` + `text-2xl font-light tracking-tight`
- Navigation: `hidden md:flex gap-6`
- Nav links: `text-sm font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors`
- CTA button: `bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-4 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-primary/90`
```

### **Hero Section**
```tsx
Hero Container:
- Layout: `py-20 px-4`
- Max width: `max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center`
- Background: `bg-gradient-to-b from-background to-background/50`

Hero Content:
- Main headline: `text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6`
- Subheadline: `text-xl md:text-2xl text-muted-foreground mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto`
- CTA button: `bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-8 py-4 rounded-md text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-primary/90`
- Secondary CTA: `text-primary hover:underline ml-6`

Hero Visual:
- Container: `mt-12 relative`
- Screenshot: `rounded-lg shadow-2xl border border-border`
- Overlay: `absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-background/20 to-transparent`
```

### **Features Section**
```tsx
Features Container:
- Layout: `py-20 px-4 bg-card/50`
- Max width: `max-w-6xl mx-auto`
- Section header: `text-center mb-16`

Section Header:
- Title: `text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4`
- Subtitle: `text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto`

Features Grid:
- Layout: `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8`
- Feature card: `bg-card rounded-lg p-6 border border-border hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow`
- Icon: `h-12 w-12 text-primary mb-4`
- Title: `text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2`
- Description: `text-muted-foreground`

Key Features:
1. Crypto Payments (Bitcoin icon)
2. Dark UI (Moon icon)
3. Multi-Payment (CreditCard icon)
4. Real-time Analytics (BarChart icon)
5. Employee Management (Users icon)
6. Inventory Tracking (Package icon)
```

### **Pricing Section**
```tsx
Pricing Container:
- Layout: `py-20 px-4`
- Max width: `max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center`

Pricing Header:
- Title: `text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4`
- Subtitle: `text-xl text-muted-foreground mb-16`

Pricing Grid:
- Layout: `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto`
- Pricing card: `bg-card rounded-lg p-8 border border-border relative`
- Popular badge: `absolute -top-4 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium`

Pricing Card Structure:
- Plan name: `text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2`
- Price: `text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-1`
- Billing cycle: `text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-6`
- Features list: `space-y-3 mb-8`
- Feature item: `flex items-center gap-3`
- Check icon: `h-5 w-5 text-primary`
- Feature text: `text-sm text-foreground`
- CTA button: `w-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-primary/90`

Pricing Tiers:
1. Free: $0/month
2. Basic: $29/month (Popular)
3. Pro: $99/month
```

### **Footer**
```tsx
Footer Container:
- Layout: `py-12 px-4 bg-card border-t border-border`
- Max width: `max-w-6xl mx-auto`

Footer Content:
- Grid: `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8`
- Company section: `col-span-1 md:col-span-2`
- Logo: Same as header
- Description: `text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-4 max-w-md`
- Links sections: `space-y-4`
- Section title: `text-sm font-semibold text-foreground mb-3`
- Link: `text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-colors`

Footer Bottom:
- Container: `mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-border flex items-center justify-between`
- Copyright: `text-sm text-muted-foreground`
- Social links: `flex gap-4`
```

