## **ðŸ“‹ Template 2: Onboarding Flow**

### **Layout Structure**
```tsx
Onboarding Container:
- Same as registration: `min-h-screen bg-background flex items-center justify-center p-8`
- Card: `w-full max-w-2xl bg-card rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8`

Header Section:
- Same logo styling as registration
- Welcome message: `text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2`
- Step description: `text-muted-foreground mb-8`

Progress Indicator:
- Same as registration multi-step form
- Shows current step in onboarding process
- Steps: Welcome â†’ Admin Setup â†’ Business Setup â†’ Payment Setup
```

### **Business Setup Form**
```tsx
Form Layout:
- Same form styling as registration
- Section groups: `space-y-8`
- Section headers: `text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-4`

Business Information:
- Business name: Required field
- Industry: Select dropdown
- Business type: Radio buttons
- Address: Multiple fields
- Phone/Email: Contact information

Business Branding:
- Logo upload: `border-2 border-dashed border-border rounded-lg p-8 text-center`
- Color scheme: Color picker (optional)
- Business hours: Time inputs

Tax & Legal:
- Tax ID: Optional field
- Business registration: Optional
- Terms acceptance: Required checkbox
```

### **Payment Setup Form**
```tsx
Payment Configuration:
- Same form styling
- Payment methods: Checkbox group
- Wallet addresses: Optional text inputs
- Provider settings: Expandable sections

Payment Methods:
- Cash: Always enabled
- Credit Cards: Stripe integration
- Bitcoin: Wallet address
- Lightning: Provider setup
- USDT: Wallet addresses
- Mercado Pago: Regional option

Integration Testing:
- Test connection buttons
- Status indicators: `text-primary` (connected), `text-muted-foreground` (not configured)
- Help text: `text-sm text-muted-foreground`
```

### **Navigation**
```tsx
Navigation Buttons:
- Same button styling as registration
- Back button: `bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground`
- Next button: `bg-primary text-primary-foreground`
- Skip option: `text-primary hover:underline`
- Progress saving: Auto-save with indicator
```

