## **ðŸ“‹ Template 3: Content Pages**

### **Layout Structure**
```tsx
Content Page Container:
- Header: Same as landing page
- Main: `max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12`
- Sidebar: `w-64 space-y-6` (optional)
- Footer: Same as landing page

Content Header:
- Page title: `text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4`
- Breadcrumb: `text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-8`
- Last updated: `text-xs text-muted-foreground`
```

### **About Page**
```tsx
About Sections:
- Company story: `prose prose-invert max-w-none`
- Mission/Vision: `bg-card rounded-lg p-6 border border-border`
- Team section: `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6`
- Team member: `bg-card rounded-lg p-4 text-center`
- Member photo: `w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4`
- Member name: `text-lg font-semibold text-foreground`
- Member role: `text-sm text-muted-foreground`
```

### **Pricing Page**
```tsx
Pricing Detailed:
- Same pricing cards as landing page
- Feature comparison table: `w-full border-collapse`
- Table header: `bg-card border-b border-border`
- Table cell: `p-4 border-b border-border`
- Check mark: `text-primary`
- FAQ section: `space-y-4`
- FAQ item: `bg-card rounded-lg p-4 border border-border`
```

### **Features Page**
```tsx
Features Detailed:
- Feature showcase: `space-y-16`
- Feature section: `grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center`
- Feature content: `space-y-4`
- Feature title: `text-2xl font-bold text-foreground`
- Feature description: `text-muted-foreground`
- Feature image: `rounded-lg shadow-lg border border-border`
- Feature list: `space-y-2`
- List item: `flex items-center gap-3`
```

### **Help/Support Pages**
```tsx
Help Layout:
- Sidebar navigation: Same as dashboard sidebar styling
- Help categories: Collapsible sections
- Search bar: `w-full h-10 px-4 rounded-md border border-input bg-background`
- Article list: `space-y-2`
- Article link: `block p-3 rounded-md hover:bg-accent transition-colors`
- Article content: `prose prose-invert max-w-none`
- Code blocks: `bg-card p-4 rounded-md border border-border`
```

### **Legal Pages**
```tsx
Legal Layout:
- Same content page structure
- Legal navigation: `sticky top-24 space-y-2`
- Legal section: `space-y-6`
- Section header: `text-xl font-semibold text-foreground border-b border-border pb-2`
- Legal text: `prose prose-invert max-w-none`
- Effective date: `text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-6`
- Contact info: `bg-card rounded-lg p-4 border border-border`
```

